with you while you euthanize.

00:57:36.797 --> 00:57:37.630 align:middle line:90%
They won't help you.

00:57:37.630 --> 00:57:40.210 align:middle line:84%
That's not legal, but they'll
be in the room with you

00:57:40.210 --> 00:57:41.180 align:middle line:90%
while you do it.

00:57:41.180 --> 00:57:45.140 align:middle line:84%
So I was really looking for a
Hail Mary pass at that point.

00:57:45.140 --> 00:57:50.280 align:middle line:84%
>> I started to look actively
for help outside the medical

00:57:50.280 --> 00:57:51.080 align:middle line:90%
establishment.

00:57:51.080 --> 00:57:53.340 align:middle line:84%
So I started-- because
I'm a software developer,

00:57:53.340 --> 00:57:56.710 align:middle line:84%
and I do a lot of internet, so
internet is like home for me.

00:57:56.710 --> 00:57:57.700 align:middle line:90%
So I started browsing.

00:57:57.700 --> 00:58:01.600 align:middle line:84%
I started finding people
with similar stories,

00:58:01.600 --> 00:58:05.830 align:middle line:84%
and then I met a lady
who became my friend,

00:58:05.830 --> 00:58:07.720 align:middle line:90%
my girlfriend, Natalie.

00:58:07.720 --> 00:58:13.750 align:middle line:84%
So she introduced
me to cannabis,

00:58:13.750 --> 00:58:16.600 align:middle line:84%
and that was, to
me, the first point

00:58:16.600 --> 00:58:20.040 align:middle line:84%
that I actually
learned that there

00:58:20.040 --> 00:58:28.210 align:middle line:84%
was hope, because after
I tried it, I fell asleep

00:58:28.210 --> 00:58:32.410 align:middle line:84%
after about four or
five years of insomnia.

00:58:32.410 --> 00:58:37.090 align:middle line:84%
All I needed from my doctor,
whom I talked to five years

00:58:37.090 --> 00:58:41.660 align:middle line:84%
previous to that experience--
the doctor who has been trained

00:58:41.660 --> 00:58:46.280 align:middle line:84%
to understand humans, to relieve
them from their suffering--

00:58:46.280 --> 00:58:48.410 align:middle line:84%
