00:58:51.770 --> 00:58:55.700 align:middle line:90%
to heal stress and insomnia.

00:58:55.700 --> 00:58:58.850 align:middle line:84%
And then I had to go
through all the conflict--

00:58:58.850 --> 00:59:02.300 align:middle line:84%
to lose my family, to
lose everything, my job--

00:59:02.300 --> 00:59:05.720 align:middle line:84%
to meet that lady who is not a
doctor at all, who doesn't even

00:59:05.720 --> 00:59:09.440 align:middle line:84%
have a bachelor
education, but she gave me

00:59:09.440 --> 00:59:11.040 align:middle line:90%
the gift of cannabis.

00:59:11.040 --> 00:59:11.960 align:middle line:90%
And I fell asleep.

00:59:11.960 --> 00:59:17.780 align:middle line:84%
>> At that point I
thought that I was clean.

00:59:17.780 --> 00:59:19.020 align:middle line:90%
My life changed so much.

00:59:19.020 --> 00:59:22.160 align:middle line:84%
I went to my 13th
treatment center.

00:59:22.160 --> 00:59:24.890 align:middle line:84%
All this time they're saying
they're bringing doctors

00:59:24.890 --> 00:59:27.170 align:middle line:84%
into all these places to
prescribe me my methadone,

00:59:27.170 --> 00:59:28.670 align:middle line:84%
