00:59:42.110 --> 00:59:45.110 align:middle line:84%
Just be grateful for
where you've come from.

00:59:45.110 --> 00:59:46.280 align:middle line:90%
You're a miracle.

00:59:46.280 --> 00:59:48.440 align:middle line:84%
So I met my husband
in 12 step rooms.

00:59:48.440 --> 00:59:51.320 align:middle line:84%
He's a recovering addict,
alcoholic, as well--

00:59:51.320 --> 00:59:52.640 align:middle line:90%
my now husband.

00:59:52.640 --> 00:59:54.377 align:middle line:84%
And we became
really good friends.

00:59:54.377 --> 00:59:56.210 align:middle line:84%
I met him when I first
got out of treatment.

00:59:56.210 --> 00:59:59.320 align:middle line:84%
We were friends for years, and
we ended up getting married.

00:59:59.320 --> 01:00:04.190 align:middle line:84%
And once we were married, I
