01:00:10.790 --> 01:00:16.040 align:middle line:84%
My brain was saying it's been
too many years, and my brain,

01:00:16.040 --> 01:00:20.180 align:middle line:84%
my body, my soul, my spirit
was just in absolute havoc.

01:00:20.180 --> 01:00:24.410 align:middle line:84%
>> I started listening to some
podcasts with a man named Dr.

01:00:24.410 --> 01:00:30.690 align:middle line:84%
Christopher Ryan, and he was the
first clear intelligent voice

01:00:30.690 --> 01:00:34.460 align:middle line:84%
