psychedelics in another way,

01:00:34.460 --> 01:00:38.990 align:middle line:84%
in a medicinal way, because
I had only ever viewed it

01:00:38.990 --> 01:00:42.410 align:middle line:84%
in a typical way that
our society treats it,

01:00:42.410 --> 01:00:44.940 align:middle line:84%
where I wasn't very
interested in that.

01:00:44.940 --> 01:00:47.330 align:middle line:84%
So I reached out to
Chris, and Chris said,

01:00:47.330 --> 01:00:50.510 align:middle line:84%
I don't know you very well, so
