I would probably do ayahuasca.

01:00:55.100 --> 01:00:58.940 align:middle line:90%
I couldn't get to Peru.

01:00:58.940 --> 01:01:02.960 align:middle line:84%
I couldn't even get from
my bed to my commode,

01:01:02.960 --> 01:01:05.600 align:middle line:84%
