His brother is a doctor.

01:02:05.270 --> 01:02:08.810 align:middle line:84%
They were reaching out, and
somebody told them about Gabor

01:02:08.810 --> 01:02:09.740 align:middle line:90%
Maté.

01:02:09.740 --> 01:02:11.587 align:middle line:84%
In one week, three
