01:02:50.450 --> 01:02:52.640 align:middle line:84%
So a couple of months
later, I went to Mexico,

01:02:52.640 --> 01:02:55.490 align:middle line:84%
and I did my first
ayahuasca ceremony.

01:02:55.490 --> 01:02:59.060 align:middle line:84%
>> With ayahuasca, I
realized that I finally found

01:02:59.060 --> 01:03:01.070 align:middle line:84%
the teacher that
I needed in life.

01:03:01.070 --> 01:03:03.500 align:middle line:84%
The ayahuasca
knocked on my heart.

01:03:03.500 --> 01:03:08.440 align:middle line:84%
A lot of things of the mind--
the mind just shut down.

01:03:08.440 --> 01:03:13.390 align:middle line:84%
The mind, after that
night, was quiet.

01:03:13.390 --> 01:03:15.800 align:middle line:90%
It became quiet.

01:03:15.800 --> 01:03:20.700 align:middle line:84%
It stopped rambling about
small things, about whatever it

01:03:20.700 --> 01:03:23.760 align:middle line:84%
was rumbling before,
about unreasonable things,

01:03:23.760 --> 01:03:26.160 align:middle line:84%
endless stories,
endless scenarios.

01:03:26.160 --> 01:03:29.820 align:middle line:84%
It eliminated all
panic attacks, so I

01:03:29.820 --> 01:03:31.870 align:middle line:90%
have no panic attacks anymore.

01:03:31.870 --> 01:03:34.340 align:middle line:90%
I have no anxiety anymore.

01:03:34.340 --> 01:03:36.090 align:middle line:84%
I don't even know how
it's possible for me

01:03:36.090 --> 01:03:38.490 align:middle line:90%
now to have them.

01:03:38.490 --> 01:03:42.780 align:middle line:84%
It's not something that
somebody takes a book,

01:03:42.780 --> 01:03:44.970 align:middle line:84%
