it with this mind,

01:03:44.970 --> 01:03:47.640 align:middle line:84%
and makes some kind
of conclusion--

01:03:47.640 --> 01:03:48.690 align:middle line:90%
logical conclusion.

01:03:48.690 --> 01:03:50.700 align:middle line:90%
It's not about that.

01:03:50.700 --> 01:03:55.070 align:middle line:84%
It's a direct
experiential learning.

01:03:55.070 --> 01:03:56.670 align:middle line:90%
>> What can I say?

01:03:56.670 --> 01:03:59.010 align:middle line:84%
That's where the real
life changing began.

01:03:59.010 --> 01:04:01.710 align:middle line:90%
It's not an escape.

01:04:01.710 --> 01:04:05.490 align:middle line:84%
Everything I used was
to numb and to escape.

01:04:05.490 --> 01:04:07.980 align:middle line:84%
Any plant medicine,
any plant teaching

01:04:07.980 --> 01:04:13.770 align:middle line:84%
is going to teach you truth,
and clarity, and connection.

01:04:13.770 --> 01:04:17.250 align:middle line:84%
And it's the exact
opposite of what I

01:04:17.250 --> 01:04:20.120 align:middle line:90%
was seeking for so many years.

01:04:20.120 --> 01:04:25.910 align:middle line:84%
You can come back from the pain
that you've been running from.

01:04:25.910 --> 01:04:27.155 align:middle line:90%
You can stop running.

01:04:27.155 --> 01:04:29.250 align:middle line:90%
And this has helped me do it.

01:04:29.250 --> 01:04:30.650 align:middle line:90%
I have liver disease.

01:04:30.650 --> 01:04:34.580 align:middle line:84%
