01:05:02.870 --> 01:05:04.050 align:middle line:90%
And I said three spirits?

01:05:04.050 --> 01:05:06.320 align:middle line:84%
He said, did you ever
have any abortions?

01:05:06.320 --> 01:05:08.570 align:middle line:90%
And I said, yes, I had two.

01:05:08.570 --> 01:05:11.210 align:middle line:84%
