try and let them be at peace,

01:05:32.910 --> 01:05:33.710 align:middle line:90%
and go.

01:05:33.710 --> 01:05:35.270 align:middle line:84%
He said, I think
after they leave

01:05:35.270 --> 01:05:37.880 align:middle line:90%
your period could come back.

01:05:37.880 --> 01:05:39.650 align:middle line:90%
And I was just looking at him.

01:05:39.650 --> 01:05:41.420 align:middle line:84%
I had just started
ayahuasca and started

01:05:41.420 --> 01:05:44.570 align:middle line:84%
working with the shaman,
and I was like, OK.

01:05:44.570 --> 01:05:47.480 align:middle line:84%
Then I'm just hearing my
addiction specialist's voice.

01:05:47.480 --> 01:05:50.050 align:middle line:84%
Lisa, just trust, just trust,
just trust, just trust.

01:05:50.050 --> 01:05:52.220 align:middle line:90%
And I'm like OK.

01:05:52.220 --> 01:05:54.740 align:middle line:84%
So I worked on this
over a two week period.

01:05:54.740 --> 01:05:56.540 align:middle line:90%
I did about 10 ceremonies.

01:05:56.540 --> 01:05:57.800 align:middle line:90%
I'd done nine ceremonies.

01:05:57.800 --> 01:06:03.470 align:middle line:84%
I was leaving the next morning
from Mexico on a 7:30 AM water

01:06:03.470 --> 01:06:04.910 align:middle line:90%
taxi.

01:06:04.910 --> 01:06:07.560 align:middle line:84%
And he came to me, and he said,
Lisa, we worked really hard.

01:06:07.560 --> 01:06:09.875 align:middle line:84%
He said we need to do one
more ceremony tonight.

01:06:09.875 --> 01:06:11.750 align:middle line:84%
