private ceremony for you.

01:06:11.750 --> 01:06:14.390 align:middle line:84%
There's still one release
that has to happen.

01:06:14.390 --> 01:06:16.970 align:middle line:90%
I was like, I can't do it.

01:06:16.970 --> 01:06:18.680 align:middle line:84%
I got to go back to
my life tomorrow,

01:06:18.680 --> 01:06:20.930 align:middle line:90%
and there's absolutely no way.

01:06:20.930 --> 01:06:25.250 align:middle line:84%
Well, I ended up trusting
and doing this last ceremony.

01:06:25.250 --> 01:06:28.370 align:middle line:84%
And after the ceremony, he
said, OK, our work is done.

01:06:28.370 --> 01:06:30.890 align:middle line:84%
And I was flying
home on the plane,

01:06:30.890 --> 01:06:34.960 align:middle line:84%
