01:06:37.700 --> 01:06:39.740 align:middle line:90%
And I've had it ever since.

01:06:39.740 --> 01:06:43.070 align:middle line:84%
So I came home, and I
told my mom this story.

01:06:43.070 --> 01:06:44.962 align:middle line:84%
